    "Qualitative Data AnalysisA total of 2 authors (TFW and FH) separately coded each text response.",
    "The answers from GPT-4 were analyzed inductively and iteratively according to Mayring's [21] qualitative content analysis, as described previously by our group [22].",
    "The goal of the analysis was defined in line with the answers to the examination questions.",
    "For the main category, we used the correct or incorrect answer to the question, then further focused primarily on incorrect answers.In the answer texts, individual reasoning was categorized according to Bloom's taxonomy as revised by Krathwohl [8].",
